how to install scm tools?

1. browse https://jazz.net/downloads/rational-team-concert
2. click the proper version suitable for your server, then click "All Downloads"
3. browse to "Plain .zip Files", "SCM Tools"
4. download "Linux x86-64(size)"
5. unzip download .zip file
6. copy everything in jazz/scmtools/eclipse/ to /root/bin/
7. edit /root/bin/scm.ini , uncomment line #2 and #3, replace line #3 as: /opt/ibm/java/jre/bin/java 
8. edit /root/bin/scm.ini , replace java heap size 512M to 3072M

or you can read online https://github.com/lospringliu/docker-gitrtc
